Background Color
=====================

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="background-color:powderblue;">
<h1 style="background-color:yellow">HTML style</h1>
<p style="background-color: white;">background color</p>
</body>
</html>

Text Color
=============

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="background-color:powderblue;">
    <h1 style="color:blueviolet">HTML style</h1>
    <p style="color:;">background color</p>
</body>
</html>

Fonts
========
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="background-color:powderblue;">



    <h1 style="font-family:verdanda;">HTML style</h1>
    <p style="font-family:courier;">This is a paragraph.</p>


</body>
</html>



Text Size
============

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="background-color:powderblue;">



    <h1 style="font-size:300%;">HTML style</h1>
    <p style="font-size:160%;">This is a paragraph.</p>


</body>
</html>


Text Alignment
===================

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="background-color:powderblue;">



    <h1 style="text-align: center;">HTML style</h1>
    <p style="text-align: left;">This is a paragraph.</p>
    <p style="text-align: right;">This is a paragraph.</p>



</body>
</html>
